            "description": "Create a new package product (bundle of multiple products).\n\n**Package Fields:**\n- productType: Must be 'package'\n- packageItems: Array of products with productId and quantity\n- price: Package price (should be less than sum of items for savings)\n\n**Auto-calculated:**\n- packageDetails.totalItemsCount\n- packageDetails.originalTotalPrice\n- packageDetails.savings\n- packageDetails.savingsPercentage"
          },
